{"tid":1797882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位優秀既香港警察 聰明既藍絲 入來睇睇","createTime":"2019-12-25T18:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T23:51:36.000Z","uid":134033,"like":147,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"14dd593d5ab859d48094da5df8f63e3d75d4b784","tid":1797882,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T18:28:51.000Z","msg":"人地大陸奶共產黨  你地奶共產黨 <br />\n<br />\n人地奶到有幾十 成百億身家<br />\n<br />\n你地奶到貼地 都仲係窮閪窮狗一個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地成世人活到中年  <br />\n<br />\n一個月賺得果一萬幾千都算<br />\n<br />\n人蠢又要廢  一事無成  取個豬閪 嫁個廢老<br />\n<br />\n做你仔女真係無陰公   悲！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地斬人 撞人 被打 被起底 最多先袋得果五六十萬<br />\n<br />\n小弟不才  一個星期就賺到  願出一百萬<br />\n<br />\n你地肯跪地下  扮狗叫 吠兩聲  柯下屎尿<br />\n<br />\n即刻開支票比你   我好愛護動物<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後生既  出賣道德倫理做隻狗察<br />\n<br />\n頂盡比你都係得個十萬一個月<br />\n<br />\n家破人亡 妻離子散 冇哂朋友  <br />\n<br />\n先搵到個十皮野  住個破爛狗屋 渣垃圾車<br />\n<br />\n取個綠帽妻   短撚夫     更悲！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老豆老母生到你 矮進樣 都算<br />\n<br />\n連個腦都毅進埋   枝槍仲高過你個人<br />\n<br />\n搞咁多野 最後咪又 窮狗一隻<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚同情你地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">知唔知最緊要係咩</span> <br />\n<br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">良知</span></span>阿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人又廢 錢又冇 腦又殘</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢D都唔係最緊要</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連做人最不可缺既<span style=\"color: gold;\">良知</span>都冇埋</span><br />\n<br />\n屌 死撚左佢啦  阻礙人類進步 <br />\n<br />\n地球既泥土都未必肯吸你地既養份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4cb6ac32e52aab14a114eef25dd489c03f74f4","tid":1797882,"uid":134033,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T18:30:22.000Z","msg":"推阿 比班仆街睇清自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8ba6ea08d363238e90ad264b795a51dbbde312","tid":1797882,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T18:32:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417e0b5d0ae0ea21c3d22d11b11d4be8aa35e1d3","tid":1797882,"uid":187799,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T18:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多人以為自己奶中共鞋底就可以飛黃騰達<br />\n殊不知而家單係奶春袋既已經有十四億人<br />\n最慘係仲以為呢種低級奴才好馨香<br />\n<br />\n香港人贏，被清算<br />\n香港人輸，被取代<br />\n真係唔傻到貼地既都唔做"},{"pid":"695c40348ff03e0fda74e1bd3abc3a46b7488d86","tid":1797882,"uid":134033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"417e0b5d0ae0ea21c3d22d11b11d4be8aa35e1d3","tid":1797882,"uid":187799,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T1